      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OUR LITTLE FORCE (1) has missed the frame at his last two but did run well three back when third (23.15) in a Grade 6 at this track. Can turn form around here. LIFE OF RILEY (2) ran below best last time finishing fifth (20.57) over 342m at Angle Park from Box 4. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from four starts. Has ability and can atone. BRINK AND BACK (7) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at this track over 400m behind Sponsorship (23.37) in a Grade 6. Was a winner prior to that. Form is hard to fault from this box, with a win and three minor placings from four starts. Can do much better this time. ELLSWORTH (4) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
